{"tid":1747851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李安然大律師教你被捕後面對警察的「救命招」","createTime":"2019-11-23T11:45:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T12:15:47.000Z","uid":62487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"316a9d90068e6ce15f8d9a9dd386f0238839d4fc","tid":1747851,"uid":62487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:45:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RvyMaYBa1hE&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;app=desktop\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRvyMaYBa1hE%26feature%3Dyoutu.be%26app%3Ddesktop&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpG0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=12d5cdbf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RvyMaYBa1hE&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;app=desktop</a><br />\n<br />\n被捕第一件事係冷靜<br />\n唔好驚到瀨屎<br />\n亦唔好比憤怒沖昏頭腦<br />\n保持冷靜應對<br />\n<br />\n分享你知道嘅被捕需知<br />\n叫全部人唔好講任何野<br />\n坐爆48,安全離開<br />\n<br />\n警察拉你入去唯一嘅目的就係告鳩你<br />\n無論佢對你點好<br />\n講過乜都係為此而服務<br />\n<br />\n謹記唔好講任何野<br />\n無論係對住任何人<br />\n黑警(屈打成招)<br />\n白警(甜言蜜語)<br />\n家屬(你屋企人on9)<br />\n同倉嘅被捕者(當中可能混入警察或者爆響口)<br />\n<br />\n律師唔知,希望有人講下<br />\n因為諗返起無間道入面劉德華就係扮律師<br />\n告入咗個黑社會"},{"pid":"77ad77ad007670450966ae291e409dd19d362b36","tid":1747851,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:46:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"45dc2130e9aef3fe0ade4ac8b6007677269b4e14","tid":1747851,"uid":43178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:48:34.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f1dbd2552e78a8db995244741b5affd71212de7","tid":1747851,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T12:15:47.000Z","msg":"真係要小心同倉既人"}]}